125
00:06:09.695 --> 00:06:11.270
yes, of course you can say yes.

126
00:06:11.270 --> 00:06:13.685
I'm not saying you can't say yes to anything.

127
00:06:13.685 --> 00:06:17.960
But if it's a bit of a loaded question with a lot of considerations,

128
00:06:17.960 --> 00:06:20.720
don't just say yes, but say, yes,

129
00:06:20.720 --> 00:06:24.350
we can do that or we can do it this way or I don't know about that.

130
00:06:24.350 --> 00:06:27.860
This is the opportunity where you get into being a consultant.

131
00:06:27.860 --> 00:06:29.510
You can say, "Yes,

132
00:06:29.510 --> 00:06:31.310
I can do that, but how about this?"

133
00:06:31.310 --> 00:06:33.335
Or have you considered this?

134
00:06:33.335 --> 00:06:36.440
Again, clients will really appreciate this.

135
00:06:36.440 --> 00:06:38.325
The final point is,

136
00:06:38.325 --> 00:06:40.775
if you don't know the solution, admit it,

137
00:06:40.775 --> 00:06:43.910
