00:06:52.385 --> 00:06:53.750
I'd be happy to learn it.

143
00:06:53.750 --> 00:06:55.080
Here's what I can do.

144
00:06:55.080 --> 00:06:56.825
You can say no for sure,

145
00:06:56.825 --> 00:06:58.100
